@startuml
title Object lifecycle: Attendance record
[*] --> MaterializedAbsent : session attendance is materialized
MaterializedAbsent --> BotPresent : voice sync sees student in channel
MaterializedAbsent --> ManualPresent : teacher marks present
MaterializedAbsent --> ManualAbsentExcused : teacher marks excused
BotPresent --> ManualPresent : teacher edits bot result
BotPresent --> ManualAbsentExcused : teacher edits bot result
ManualPresent --> ManualAbsentExcused : teacher edits attendance
ManualAbsentExcused --> ManualPresent : teacher edits attendance
BotPresent --> FeeCharged : fee projection synced
ManualPresent --> FeeCharged : fee projection synced
ManualAbsentExcused --> FeeNotCharged : fee projection synced
FeeCharged --> [*]
FeeNotCharged --> [*]
@enduml
